🛠️ Enterprise Tools
A curated collection of strategic frameworks, ROI calculators, and presales resources designed to bridge the gap between complex AI architecture and tangible business value.

📖 Overview
This repository serves as a library for the technical and strategic assets I have developed to support enterprise AI sales cycles. These tools are built to move the conversation from abstract technical capability to measurable organizational ROI. Whether scoping a complex multi-agent deployment or facilitating a discovery workshop, these resources are designed to turn ambiguity into a clear business case.

📁 Repository Contents
1. Decoupled Agent Frameworks
Whitepaper: An architectural blueprint for closing the corporate "scalability gap" by decoupling foundational agent infrastructure from instruction layers. This approach allows organizations to build reusable, resilient AI engines that scale across diverse departmental use cases.

2. ROI & Value Quantification Models
Healthcare ROI Calculator: An interactive HTML/JavaScript framework mapping financial value across revenue cycle acceleration, clinical capacity recovery, and audit risk mitigation.

RAG Impact Calculator: A benchmark-driven utility that projects real-time time savings and ROI. These tools are designed to be used in live prospect conversations, allowing stakeholders to plug in their own assumptions and build their own internal business cases.

3. Presales & Workshop Resources
Workshop Guide & Framework: A comprehensive resource for guiding organizations through a structured AI adoption workshop. Includes standardized prompt-engineering templates, evaluation metrics, and customer-specific agent training modules.

💡 Philosophy: Building for the Rule, Not the Exception
My approach to enterprise SE work is rooted in the belief that AI should be built for scale. Instead of solving isolated problems with "one-off" solutions, I focus on:

Standardization: Creating reusable templates that can be repurposed across an entire organization.

Evidence-Based Scoping: Using industry benchmarks (McKinsey, Gartner) to ground ROI projections in reality.

Transparency: Building tools that empower the prospect to take ownership of their own business case, fostering trust and accelerating procurement.

🚀 Usage
Whitepapers: Available as PDFs.

ROI Calculators: Designed to be run locally; can be embedded into demo environments or shared as standalone web utilities.

Workshop Resources: Provided as templates to be customized per customer profile.

Strategy-driven SE assets for the modern enterprise.
